{"tid":944794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「小鳥爆開了」一人一句/幾句想同林鄭/其他高官講嘅說話","createTime":"2018-12-17T11:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T11:52:48.000Z","uid":225828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebcd669cf4e9be53633ee7842796e0230b056369","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:47:32.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母啦林鄭,山竹都唔撚畀人放假,將打工仔當狗咁撚,講埋唒啲咩希望僱主會體諒依啲攞景贈興嘢,仲話自己係上帝叫你參選,咁撚冇人性我就話你係魔鬼代言人幫魔鬼暫時管理住香港喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又將啲私人恩怨擺落社會政策到,死唔跟薯片嗰套搞到派嗰四千都派到柒吓柒咁,你唔好逼人叫你做柒婆啦好嘛,你唔要面你屋企人都要面㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到自己咁打得,連照顧自己日常生活買廁紙用八達通都唔識,弱智人士都醒個你啦,高分低能！自己咁高學歴要聽個小學畢業嘅點嚟點去,讀屎片㗎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人哋國家元首互相角力,好心你就縮返入你太婆個閪喥啦,莊閒都唔識分,把閪口剩係識噴埋啲咩「美國行單邊主義」、「美國唔好干涉香港內政嘅」嘅狗屎,你主子有冇批准你奶佢鞋底呀Carriage Lam 林馬車？都仲未提你老母臭/湊 大你,你竟然走去做宦官？以為同人哋侵侵咁高咁大？喂餵,企開啲啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我真係好鄧葉劉唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解當年畀麒麟撞嘅係佢,唔係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聖誕節就到喇,如果聖誕老人畀我一份聖誕禮物,我希望佢可以用鹿車車鳩你,然後叫埋啲咩嘢聖誕小精靈、寵物小精靈、數碼暴龍同埋妖怪手錶一齊代天道揼柒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後變走唒你新年啲利是錢做樹葉同埋溪錢,等你可以過一個乜鳩都冇嘅新年：Happy New Year <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b540eebd54acb716882b3fd0afcd472b5da3cf6e","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4392141a4b8c7127ce6f28dceb0cf3781e064c1b","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17377ea00577126dcef25244203006a61eaf4471","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3980b2e1859b06a783d32b3264feb5e911a1985b","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2ae21e9c5149a90fc1568d0a898dd91ee6984b","tid":944794,"uid":65397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"打完飛機有冇開心咗？"},{"pid":"a090147c6a8b519446c4f25ff66451c075815b35","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:51:48.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"391812a971d3e7096335e77afd53e96b797f3060","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:52:08.000Z","msg":"有火快屌"},{"pid":"437c2a0a67a58f2cf93ecefdd5776fb42bf97dda","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235e1ea4f42c5c4542f0b205ca766e54b70c41eb","tid":944794,"uid":225828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}